  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Accounts cum Admin Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Able to handle full set of accounts, prepare monthly closing & financial reports independently.</li><li>Maintain master data and verify transactions in accounting system.</li><li>Accounts receivable, accounts payable, fixed assets and inventory.</li><li>Prepare company tax computation and quarterly submit GST to IRAS.</li><li>Close P&L, balance sheet and prepare audit schedules. </li><li>Handle HR functions – Payroll, CPF, IR8A, recruitment, work passes for foreign workers.</li><li>Other ad-hoc duties as assigned by management. </li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong> </p><ul><li><a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"></a><a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"></a><a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"></a><a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"></a><a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"></a><a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Minimum Diploma in in Accountancy or Equivalent. </a> </li><li>Singaporean / PR </li><li>Bilingual in English & Chinese (liaise with Chinese speaking customers). </li><li>Minimum 5 years of relevant experience in full sets of Accounts.</li><li>Able to multitask and work independently.</li><li>Proficiency in Microsoft Excel and basic computer knowledge.</li><li>Hands-on experience in Microsoft Dynamics Navision software. </li><li>Able to start work immediately or in short notice is an advantage.</li><li>Working hours: 5 Working days ; Mon to Fri (8.30am-6.00pm)</li><li>Working area: Woodlands. </li><li>Qualified applicants to submit your resume to <a href=\"mailto:account@estron.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">account@estron.com.sg / </a><a href=\"mailto:alice@estron.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">lynn@estron.com.sg</a></li><li><a href=\"mailto:alice@estron.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"></a>Please state 1. Current salary 2. Expected salary 3. Reasons for leaving previous employment 4. Notice period to leave employment</li></ul><p>Applications meet the above requirements would be reviewed first. We regret that only short-listed candidates would be notified for interviews.<br />\nPlease visit our corporate website at <a href=\"http://www.estron.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">www.estron.com.sg</a></p>",
